$Id: Readme,v 1.1 2003/01/07 18:00:18 kozlik Exp $

This program sends meteorological data to users which have subscribed this
service. Program uses netgeo cache to get locator of nearest metar station.

usage:
------

  you must put this script to your html tree and use wget utility
  see wget man page for more details

  use parameter serweb_config to specifi serweb config file for example:

    send_metar.php?serweb_config=path/to/serweb/config/file/config.php


requirements:
-------------

- serweb
- phpweather 2.0 or later       (http://phpweather.sourceforge.net)


Instalation:
------------

- install phpweather to subdirectory "phpweather" in your send_metar directory
- configure phpweather, see documentation of it for more details
- change values in serweb config file
